{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":6701,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93636,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104329,"text":"Trevor Copp: When \"Dancing With the Stars\"\nfirst hit the airwaves,"},{"time":107457,"text":"that is not what it looked like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111121,"text":"Jeff and I were full-time\nballroom dance instructors"},{"time":114172,"text":"when the big TV ballroom revival hit,"},{"time":117609,"text":"and this was incredible."},{"time":121132,"text":"I mean, one day we would say \"foxtrot,\""},{"time":123760,"text":"and people were like \"Foxes trotting.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":126821,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128575,"text":"And the next day they were telling us"},{"time":130553,"text":"the finer points of a good feather step."},{"time":132965,"text":"And this blew our minds."},{"time":135342,"text":"I mean, all of the ballroom dance\ngeeking out that we had always done"},{"time":140588,"text":"on why salsa worked differently\nthan the competitive rumba"},{"time":144251,"text":"and why tango traveled unlike the waltz,"},{"time":146779,"text":"all of that just hit\nthe public consciousness,"},{"time":151383,"text":"and it changed everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153834,"text":"But running parallel to this excitement,"},{"time":156224,"text":"the excitement that suddenly,\nsomehow, we were cool --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160599,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":163044,"text":"there was also this reservation."},{"time":165914,"text":"Why this and why now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169556,"text":"Jeff Fox: When Trevor and I\nwould get together for training seminars"},{"time":172813,"text":"or just for fun,"},{"time":173996,"text":"we'd toss each other around, mix it up,"},{"time":175886,"text":"take a break from having\nto lead all the time."},{"time":178097,"text":"We even came up with a system\nfor switching lead and follow"},{"time":180891,"text":"while we were dancing,"},{"time":182066,"text":"as a way of taking turns and playing fair."},{"time":184099,"text":"It wasn't until we used that system\nas part of a performance"},{"time":187080,"text":"in a small festival"},{"time":188265,"text":"that we got an important tap\non the shoulder."},{"time":190416,"text":"Lisa O'Connell, a dramaturge\nand director of a playwright center,"},{"time":193748,"text":"pulled us aside after the show and said,"},{"time":196154,"text":"\"Do you have any idea\nhow political that was?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":198858,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200898,"text":"So that began an eight-year\ncollaboration to create a play"},{"time":203691,"text":"which not only further developed\nour system for switching"},{"time":206476,"text":"but also explored the impact\nof being locked into a single role,"},{"time":210258,"text":"and what's worse,"},{"time":211446,"text":"being defined by that single role."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213599,"text":"TC: Because, of course,"},{"time":215968,"text":"classic Latin and ballroom dancing\nisn't just a system of dancing;"},{"time":220719,"text":"it's a way of thinking, of being,"},{"time":223924,"text":"of relating to each other"},{"time":225571,"text":"that captured a whole period's values."},{"time":228599,"text":"There's one thing that stayed\nconsistent, though:"},{"time":230990,"text":"the man leads"},{"time":232340,"text":"and the woman follows."},{"time":234126,"text":"So street salsa, championship tango,\nit's all the same --"},{"time":236878,"text":"he leads, she follows."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239335,"text":"So this was gender training."},{"time":241623,"text":"You weren't just learning to dance --"},{"time":243449,"text":"you were learning to \"man\" and to \"woman.\""},{"time":247813,"text":"It's a relic."},{"time":249590,"text":"And in the way of relics,\nyou don't throw it out,"},{"time":251920,"text":"but you need to know\nthat this is the past."},{"time":254327,"text":"This isn't the present."},{"time":256866,"text":"It's like Shakespeare:\nrespect it, revive it -- great!"},{"time":259969,"text":"But know that this is history."},{"time":261479,"text":"This doesn't represent how we think today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265045,"text":"So we asked ourselves:"},{"time":266609,"text":"If you strip it all down,"},{"time":268672,"text":"what is at the core of partner dancing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":272094,"text":"JF: Well, the core principle\nof partner dancing"},{"time":274353,"text":"is that one person leads,\nthe other one follows."},{"time":277094,"text":"The machine works the same,\nregardless of who's playing which role."},{"time":280388,"text":"The physics of movement doesn't really\ngive a crap about your gender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283683,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284747,"text":"So if we were to update the existing form,"},{"time":286801,"text":"we would need to make it\nmore representative"},{"time":288919,"text":"of how we interact here, now, in 2015."},{"time":292031,"text":"When you watch ballroom,\ndon't just watch what's there."},{"time":295517,"text":"Watch what's not."},{"time":297089,"text":"The couple is always\nonly a man and a woman."},{"time":300125,"text":"Together."},{"time":301307,"text":"Only."},{"time":302603,"text":"Ever."},{"time":303778,"text":"So, same-sex and gender nonconformist\ncouples just disappear."},{"time":307884,"text":"In most mainstream international\nballroom competitions,"},{"time":310540,"text":"same-sex couples are rarely\nrecognized on the floor,"},{"time":313183,"text":"and in many cases,"},{"time":314391,"text":"the rules prohibit them completely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316152,"text":"TC: Try this: Google-image,\n\"professional Latin dancer,\""},{"time":321504,"text":"and then look for an actual Latino person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323739,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":325130,"text":"You'll be there for days."},{"time":327145,"text":"What you will get is page after page\nof white, straight Russian couples"},{"time":331194,"text":"spray-tanned to the point of mahogany."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333183,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":335108,"text":"There are no black people,\nthere are no Asians,"},{"time":337392,"text":"no mixed-race couples,"},{"time":338700,"text":"so basically, non-white people\njust disappeared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342727,"text":"Even within the white-straight-\ncouple-only paradigm --"},{"time":348008,"text":"she can't be taller,"},{"time":349413,"text":"he can't be shorter."},{"time":350905,"text":"She can't be bolder,"},{"time":353025,"text":"he can't be gentler."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355261,"text":"If you were to take a ballroom dance"},{"time":357505,"text":"and translate that into a conversation"},{"time":359822,"text":"and drop that into a movie,"},{"time":361288,"text":"we, as a culture,\nwould never stand for this."},{"time":364934,"text":"He dictates, she reacts."},{"time":368674,"text":"No relationship -- gay,\nstraight or anything --"},{"time":371703,"text":"that we would regard as remotely healthy\nor functional looks like that,"},{"time":376134,"text":"and yet somehow,"},{"time":377744,"text":"you put it on prime time,\nyou slap some makeup on it,"},{"time":380382,"text":"throw the glitter on, put it out there\nas movement, not as text,"},{"time":384832,"text":"and we, as a culture,"},{"time":386974,"text":"tune in and clap."},{"time":389805,"text":"We are applauding our own absence."},{"time":394130,"text":"Too many people have disappeared\nfrom partner dancing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398334,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442276,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448957,"text":"JF: Now, you just saw\ntwo men dancing together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":452557,"text":"And you thought it looked ..."},{"time":454412,"text":"a little strange."},{"time":456130,"text":"Interesting -- appealing, even --"},{"time":458199,"text":"but a little bit odd."},{"time":460372,"text":"Even avid followers of the same-sex\nballroom circuit can attest"},{"time":463380,"text":"that while same-sex partner dancing\ncan be dynamic and strong and exciting,"},{"time":467514,"text":"it just doesn't quite seem to fit."},{"time":470446,"text":"Aesthetically speaking,"},{"time":471687,"text":"if Alida and I take the classic\nclosed ballroom hold ..."},{"time":477637,"text":"this is considered beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482204,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484703,"text":"But why not this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":485985,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487699,"text":"See, the standard image that the leader\nmust be larger and masculine"},{"time":491391,"text":"and the follower smaller and feminine --"},{"time":493950,"text":"this is a stumbling point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495978,"text":"TC: So we wanted to look at this\nfrom a totally different angle."},{"time":501467,"text":"So, what if we could keep\nthe idea of lead and follow"},{"time":505059,"text":"but toss the idea that this\nwas connected to gender?"},{"time":508824,"text":"Further, what if a couple\ncould lead and follow each other"},{"time":513851,"text":"and then switch?"},{"time":515513,"text":"And then switch back?"},{"time":517690,"text":"What if it could be like a conversation,"},{"time":520949,"text":"taking turns listening and speaking,\njust like we do in life?"},{"time":524042,"text":"What if we could dance like that?"},{"time":528418,"text":"We call it \"Liquid Lead Dancing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":532542,"text":"JF: Let's try this with a Latin dance,"},{"time":535045,"text":"salsa."},{"time":536524,"text":"In salsa, there's a key transitional step,\ncalled the cross-body lead."},{"time":540185,"text":"We use it as punctuation\nto break up the improvisation."},{"time":542969,"text":"It can be a little tricky to spot\nif you're not used to looking for it,"},{"time":546363,"text":"so here it is."},{"time":553191,"text":"One more time for the cheap seats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554869,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":560378,"text":"And here's the action one more time,"},{"time":562407,"text":"nice and slow."},{"time":568842,"text":"Now, if we apply liquid-lead thinking\nto this transitional step,"},{"time":572953,"text":"the cross-body lead becomes a point"},{"time":574659,"text":"where the lead and the follow can switch."},{"time":576668,"text":"The person following can elect\nto take over the lead,"},{"time":579215,"text":"or the person leading can choose\nto surrender it,"},{"time":581592,"text":"essentially making it\na counter-cross-body lead."},{"time":584208,"text":"Here's how that looks in slow motion."},{"time":593913,"text":"And here's how it looked\nwhen we danced it in the opening dance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602789,"text":"With this simple tweak,\nthe dance moves from being a dictation"},{"time":606186,"text":"to a negotiation."},{"time":607761,"text":"Anyone can lead. Anyone can follow."},{"time":610278,"text":"And more importantly,\nyou can change your mind."},{"time":613523,"text":"Now, this is only one example\nof how this applies,"},{"time":615913,"text":"but once the blinkers come off,\nanything can happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619090,"text":"TC: Let's look at how Liquid Lead thinking\ncould apply to a classic waltz."},{"time":624297,"text":"Because, of course,"},{"time":625549,"text":"it isn't just a system of switching leads;"},{"time":628164,"text":"it's a way of thinking"},{"time":629354,"text":"that can actually make\nthe dance itself more efficient."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632981,"text":"So: the waltz."},{"time":634891,"text":"The waltz is a turning dance."},{"time":636984,"text":"This means that for the lead,"},{"time":638620,"text":"you spend half of the dance\ntraveling backwards,"},{"time":641856,"text":"completely blind."},{"time":643350,"text":"And because of the follower's position,"},{"time":645923,"text":"basically, no one can see\nwhere they're going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648755,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":650127,"text":"So you're out here on the floor,"},{"time":652163,"text":"and then imagine that coming right at you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654851,"text":"JF: Raaaaaah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656224,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":657772,"text":"TC: There are actually a lot\nof accidents out there"},{"time":661092,"text":"that happen as a result\nof this blind spot."},{"time":664080,"text":"But what if the partners\nwere to just allow for"},{"time":667346,"text":"a switch of posture for a moment?"},{"time":669519,"text":"A lot of accidents could be avoided."},{"time":672253,"text":"Even if one person led the whole dance\nbut allowed this switch to happen,"},{"time":677117,"text":"it would be a lot safer,"},{"time":678527,"text":"while at the same time,\noffering new aesthetics into the waltz."},{"time":682221,"text":"Because physics doesn't give a damn\nabout your gender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685678,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":688154,"text":"JF: Now, we've danced Liquid Lead\nin clubs, convention centers"},{"time":691179,"text":"and as part of \"First Dance,\"\nthe play we created with Lisa,"},{"time":694021,"text":"on stages in North America and in Europe."},{"time":696387,"text":"And it never fails to engage."},{"time":698736,"text":"I mean, beyond the unusual sight\nof seeing two men dancing together,"},{"time":702241,"text":"it always evokes and engages."},{"time":705174,"text":"But why?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":706485,"text":"The secret lies in what made\nLisa see our initial demonstration"},{"time":709604,"text":"as \"political.\""},{"time":710931,"text":"It wasn't just that we were\nswitching lead and follow;"},{"time":713530,"text":"it's that we stayed consistent\nin our presence, our personality"},{"time":716611,"text":"and our power, regardless\nof which role we were playing."},{"time":719564,"text":"We were still us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721816,"text":"And that's where the true freedom lies --"},{"time":723875,"text":"not just the freedom to switch roles,"},{"time":725888,"text":"but the freedom from being defined\nby whichever role you're playing,"},{"time":729527,"text":"the freedom to always remain\ntrue to yourself."},{"time":732457,"text":"Forget what a lead is supposed\nto look like, or a follow."},{"time":735581,"text":"Be a masculine follow"},{"time":737160,"text":"or a feminine lead."},{"time":738795,"text":"Just be yourself."},{"time":740873,"text":"Obviously, this applies\noff the dance floor as well,"},{"time":743614,"text":"but on the floor, it gives us\nthe perfect opportunity"},{"time":746177,"text":"to update an old paradigm,\nreinvigorate an old relic,"},{"time":749498,"text":"and make it more representative\nof our era and our current way of being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":754630,"text":"TC: Jeff and I dance partner dancing\nall the time with women and men"},{"time":757995,"text":"and we love it."},{"time":759407,"text":"But we dance with a consciousness\nthat this is a historic form"},{"time":763994,"text":"that can produce silence\nand produce invisibility"},{"time":768328,"text":"across the spectrum of identity\nthat we enjoy today."},{"time":771820,"text":"We invented Liquid Lead"},{"time":773338,"text":"as a way of stripping out\nall the ideas that don't belong to us"},{"time":778527,"text":"and taking partner dancing back\nto what it really always was:"},{"time":783830,"text":"the fine art of taking care of each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788829,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":908910,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}